- `gamenative-profile-ingame-invites.mdc` — Player Profile fix, in-game chat side panel, Steam game invites
- `gamenative-advanced-performance.mdc` — CPU affinity, ZRAM/memory tuning, audio latency, Wine-GE, ProtonDB badges, D8VK, input polling, huge pages, shader pre-warming, VKD3D heap tuning
